     H            Y.
     F** AARR01 ******************************
     F* DELETE  OF PLATING ACCOUNT RECEIVABLE UNIT PRICE M/F *
     F* A.IDOTA              1995.07.03      *
     F****************************** AARR01 **
     FAARNP01 UP  F      20            DISK
     FAARTL11 UF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAARWP01AO   F      52            DISK
     FAARWP01BO   F      52            DISK
     IAARNP01 AA
     I                                        1   60#SKYM
     I                                        1   40#SKYY
     I                                        5   60#SKMM
     I                                        7   80#SKDD
     I                                        9  20 #HBAN
     I                                        9  13 #HNB1
     I                                       14  18 #HNB2
     I                                       19  20 #HNB3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60YM
     I                                        1   40YY
     I                                        5   60MM
      ** PARM **
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           US     10
      ** KEY **
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #HNB1
     C                     KFLD           #HNB2
     C                     KFLD           #HNB3
      *****************************************************************
      * 削除予定日のチェック                                 MAIN   *
      *****************************************************************
     C                     Z-ADD0         YY
     C                     Z-ADD0         MM
      ** 月=１月 **
     C           UMONTH    IFEQ 01
     C           *YEAR     SUB  1         YY
     C                     Z-ADD12        MM
     C                     ELSE
      ** 月=２月 **
     C*          UMONTH    IFEQ 02
     C*          UYEAR     SUB  1         YY
     C*                    Z-ADD12        MM
     C*                    ELSE
      ** その他 **
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     YY
     C           UMONTH    SUB  1         MM
     C                     END
     C*                    END
      *
     C           YM        IFNE #SKYM
     C                     GOTO @END
     C                     END
      *****************************************************************
      * 部品マスター                                         MAIN   *
      *****************************************************************
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY1      CHAINFCEPL011             30
      *****************************************************************
      * 売掛金単価マスター存在チェック                       MAIN   *
      *****************************************************************
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY1      CHAINAARTL111             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '1'
     C                     EXCPTDT2
     C                     ELSE
      ** メッキ売掛金単価マスター削除 **
     C                     MOVEL'D'       CSSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     CSSKYY
     C                     Z-ADDUMONTH    CSSKMM
     C                     Z-ADDUDAY      CSSKDD
     C                     MOVELUS        CSKOME
     C                     UPDATAARTL111                   単価uﾇjｰ
     C                     EXCPTDT1                        kｩｮh.ﾒﾇn
     C                     DELETAARNP01                    削除WORK-F
     C                     END
      *****
     C           @END      TAG
